10
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:04,520
-克麗絲　-你好
- Clarice. - Hey.

11
00:04:39,190 --> 00:04:41,250
（行為科學組）

12
00:04:55,570 --> 00:04:56,770
找克勞福嗎？
Looking for Crawford?

13
00:04:57,040 --> 00:05:00,210
他快回來了，在他的辦公室等一會吧
He should be back soon. Why don't you wait in his office?

14
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:55,720
（比爾剝下第五個人的皮）

15
00:05:57,500 --> 00:05:58,830
史達琳
Starling.

16
00:05:59,710 --> 00:06:03,000
-克麗絲，早安　-早安，克勞福先生
- Clarice M. Good morning. - Morning, Mr. Crawford.

17
00:06:03,010 --> 00:06:06,540
抱歉突然把你召離課堂
Sorry to pull you off the course at such short notice.

18
00:06:06,540 --> 00:06:09,610
你的導師說你是班裡的高材生
Your instructors say you're in the top quarter of your class.

19
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:13,240
希望是吧，他們還沒有公佈成績
I hope so. They haven't posted any grades yet.

20
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,980
有一個任務要辦，於是我想起你
A job's come up, and I thought about you.

21
00:06:16,290 --> 00:06:18,810
這不是正式的任務，較像一份有趣的差事
Not a job, really, more of an interesting errand.

22
00:06:19,190 --> 00:06:20,250
坐下
Sit down.

23
00:06:20,890 --> 00:06:21,760
是，長官
Yes, sir.

24
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:26,300
我記得你出席過，我在維吉尼亞大學的講座
I remember you from my seminar at UVA.

25
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:31,300
你追問我本局在胡佛年代的，公民權益記錄
You grilled me on the bureau's civil rights record in the Hoover years.

26
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,430
我給了你甲等
I gave you an A.

27
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:34,130
是甲下
A minus, sir.

28
00:06:37,010 --> 00:06:40,070
雙主修，心理學及犯罪學，以優異成績畢業
Double major, psych and criminology, graduated magna.

29
00:06:40,350 --> 00:06:42,970
在瑞辛格療養院做過夏季實習
Summer internships at the Reitzinger Clinic.

30
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:47,950
它說你畢業後，想在行為科學組替我工作
It says when you graduate you want to work for me in Behavioral Science.

31
00:06:48,350 --> 00:06:50,180
是的，我很想
Yes, very much, sir. Very much.

32
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:54,260
我們正在訪問被囚禁的連環殺手
We're interviewing all serial killers in custody...

33
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:56,220
作變態行為的分析
for a psycho-behavioral profile.

34
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:59,300
