659
00:59:55,500 --> 00:59:57,630
我找過凱瑟琳・馬丁參議員
I called Senator Ruth Martin.

660
00:59:57,910 --> 01:00:00,530
她沒聽過跟你有任何協議
She never heard of any deal with you.

661
01:00:01,480 --> 01:00:03,970
他們騙你
They scammed you, Hannibal.

662
01:00:05,510 --> 01:00:06,980
出去
Stand outside.

663
01:00:08,450 --> 01:00:09,940
把門關上
And shut the door.

664
01:00:10,350 --> 01:00:11,550
巴尼
Barney.

665
01:00:17,760 --> 01:00:21,960
從沒有跟馬丁參議員作過協議，但現在有了
There never was a deal with Senator Martin, but there is now.

666
01:00:22,230 --> 01:00:23,390
是我議定的
I designed it.

667
01:00:23,670 --> 01:00:27,290
當然，我也為自己的利益，定下了一些條件
Of course, I worked in a few conditions for my own benefit as well.

668
01:00:27,640 --> 01:00:30,630
說出水牛比爾的名字
Identify Buffalo Bill by name...

669
01:00:30,910 --> 01:00:32,900
如果那個女孩及時被發現
and if the girl is found in time...

670
01:00:33,180 --> 01:00:37,370
你就會被轉送到田納西州的叢樹山州立監獄
you'll be transferred to Brushy Mountain State Prison in Tennessee.

671
01:00:38,550 --> 01:00:40,280
回答我
Answer me, Hannibal.

672
01:00:42,380 --> 01:00:43,450
你現在回答我
You answer me now...

673
01:00:43,450 --> 01:00:46,680
否則，天啊，你休想離開這個牢房
or, by God, you'll never leave this cell.

674
01:00:49,020 --> 01:00:51,190
水牛比爾是誰？
Who is Buffalo Bill?

675
01:00:52,130 --> 01:00:54,220
他的名字是路易斯
His first name is Louis.

676
01:00:54,730 --> 01:00:58,190
其餘的我只會在田納西州，親自對參議員說
I'll tell the rest to the Senator herself, but only in Tennessee.

677
01:00:58,500 --> 01:01:00,870
我也有幾個條件
And I have a few conditions of my own.

678
01:01:03,570 --> 01:01:05,600
替他梳洗一下，準備出發
Clean him up and get him ready to go.

679
01:01:06,710 --> 01:01:09,840
傑克，漢尼拔・萊達正被轉送往孟斐斯途中
Jack, Hannibal Lecter is being transferred to Memphis.

680
01:01:10,150 --> 01:01:10,780
轉送？
Transferred?

681
01:01:10,780 --> 01:01:15,820
你可有個見習生，冒參議員之名，向萊達提出一個虛假的建議？
Did you have a trainee make a phony offer to Lecter in the senator's name?

682
01:01:16,290 --> 01:01:17,980
是我的主意，我逼不得已
I rolled the dice. I had to.

683
01:01:18,320 --> 01:01:20,290
她氣瘋了
Well, she's mad as hell, Jack.

684
01:01:20,560 --> 01:01:22,350
司法部的保羅・肯度拿來了
Paul Krendler's here from Justice.

685
01:01:22,690 --> 01:01:25,390
她要求他在孟斐斯接手
She's asking him to take over in Memphis.

686
01:01:32,070 --> 01:01:35,760
（孟斐斯市國際機場）

687
01:01:50,150 --> 01:01:51,880
萊達醫生，歡迎到孟斐斯
Welcome to Memphis, Dr. Lecter.

688
01:01:52,220 --> 01:01:54,710
我是鮑爾探員，這位是派屈克警長
I'm Lieutenant Boyle. This is Sergeant Patrick.

689
01:01:55,060 --> 01:01:57,080
我們會像你待我們那麼好的
We'll treat you as good as you treat us.

690
01:01:57,360 --> 01:02:00,390
你乖乖的，就會得到舒服的待遇
You be a gentleman, you'll get three hots and a cot.

691
01:02:01,500 --> 01:02:05,230
長官，請在這裡簽名，我們作合法的移交
Sir, if you sign right here, we'll have us a legal transfer.

692
01:02:10,710 --> 01:02:12,260
用我的吧
Here, sir, use mine.

693
01:02:59,590 --> 01:03:00,450
馬丁參議員
Senator Martin...

694
01:03:01,960 --> 01:03:04,020
漢尼拔・萊達醫生
Dr. Hannibal Lecter.

695
01:03:08,830 --> 01:03:10,320
萊達醫生
Dr. Lecter...

696
01:03:10,900 --> 01:03:14,270
我帶了一份宣誓書，保證你新的權利
l've brought an affidavit guaranteeing your new rights.

697
01:03:14,640 --> 01:03:17,040
在我簽署前你要看看的
You'll want to read it before I sign.

698
01:03:20,780 --> 01:03:24,940
我不會為了小利益，而耽誤你或凱瑟琳的時間
I won't waste your time or Catherine's time bargaining for petty privileges.

699
01:03:25,210 --> 01:03:28,980
克麗絲・史達琳和克勞福，已經浪費了太多時間
Clarice Starling and Jack Crawford have wasted too much time already.

700
01:03:29,080 --> 01:03:32,590
但願他們沒有害死，那個可憐的女孩
I only pray they haven't doomed the poor girl.

701
01:03:33,720 --> 01:03:36,920
讓我幫你吧，事成後我會信任你
Let me help you now. I will trust you when it is all over.

702
01:03:37,460 --> 01:03:39,430
我答應你，保羅
You have my word. Paul.

703
01:03:42,230 --> 01:03:44,600
水牛比爾的真名是路易斯・法蘭
Buffalo Bill's real name is Louis Friend.

704
01:03:46,030 --> 01:03:49,830
我只見過他一次，1980年4 5月間由我的病人...
I met him just once. He was referred to me in April or May, 1980...

705
01:03:50,210 --> 01:03:52,730
班哲文・賴普轉介給我的
by my patient Benjamin Raspail.

706
01:03:53,080 --> 01:03:54,870
他們是愛人
They were lovers, you see.

707
01:03:55,380 --> 01:03:59,180
但賴普變得很害怕
But Raspail had become very frightened.

708
01:03:59,550 --> 01:04:02,880
看來路易斯謀殺了一個流浪漢
Apparently, Louis had murdered a transient...

709
01:04:04,750 --> 01:04:06,410
用他的皮膚做了一些東西
and done things with the skin.

710
01:04:07,490 --> 01:04:09,860
我們要他的地址和容貌特徵
We need his address and a physical description.

711
01:04:11,330 --> 01:04:12,990
告訴我，參議員...
Tell me, senator.

712
01:04:13,630 --> 01:04:15,930
你有沒有親自哺育凱瑟琳？
Did you nurse Catherine yourself?

713
01:04:16,500 --> 01:04:18,990
-什麼？　-你有沒有給她餵奶？
- What? - Did you breast-feed her?

714
01:04:19,330 --> 01:04:21,600
-混帳　-我有的
- Now, wait a minute! - Yes. I did.

715
01:04:22,000 --> 01:04:24,000
令你的乳頭變得堅挺，是嗎？
Toughened your nipples, didn't it?

716
01:04:24,310 --> 01:04:25,140
你這個混蛋！
You son of a bitch!

717
01:04:25,810 --> 01:04:29,440
把人的腿切除，他仍感到振奮
Amputate a man's leg, and he can still feel it tickling.

718
01:04:29,850 --> 01:04:33,040
告訴我，媽媽，當你的小女兒被殺時
Tell me, Mom, when your little girl is on the slab...

719
01:04:33,350 --> 01:04:34,680
你哪裡會感到振奮？
where will it tickle you?

720
01:04:35,750 --> 01:04:38,980
把這個畜生帶回巴爾的摩
Take this thing back to Baltimore.

721
01:04:40,090 --> 01:04:42,890
五英尺十英吋，身材魁悟，約一百八十磅
Five-foot-ten, strongly built, about 180 pounds.

722
01:04:43,260 --> 01:04:45,730
金髮，淺藍色眼睛
Hair, blond. Eyes, pale blue.

723
01:04:46,030 --> 01:04:47,150
他現在大約三十五歲
He'd be about 35 now.

724
01:04:47,460 --> 01:04:50,190
他聲稱住在費城，可能是說謊
He said he lived in Philadelphia but may have lied.

725
01:04:50,570 --> 01:04:52,120
我只記得這麼多了，媽
That's all I can remember, Mom.

726
01:04:52,500 --> 01:04:55,030
若我再想起什麼，我會通知你的
But if I think of any more, I will let you know.

727
01:04:57,640 --> 01:04:59,940
參議員，還有一件事
Oh, and senator, just one more thing:

728
01:05:02,440 --> 01:05:04,070
你的套裝很漂亮
Love your suit.

729
01:05:06,380 --> 01:05:09,180
與馬丁參議員，在今天較早前的會面中
In a meeting earlier today with Senator Ruth Martin...

730
01:05:09,550 --> 01:05:13,680
萊達醫生同意協助追緝水牛比爾
Dr. Lecter agreed to help in the investigation to find Buffalo Bill.

731
01:05:11,580 --> 01:05:15,250
（謝爾比縣法院大樓）

732
01:05:16,190 --> 01:05:17,990
-你扮演什麼角色？　-我對萊達醫生的...
- How do you fit in? - My unique insight...

733
01:05:18,360 --> 01:05:20,120
獨特觸覺促成了這次突破
into Lecter made the breakthrough.

734
01:05:20,500 --> 01:05:21,480
水牛比爾叫什麼名字？
Buffalo Bill's name?

735
01:05:21,760 --> 01:05:25,390
這是目前有關當局的秘密
His name is now a matter of record with the proper authorities.

736
01:05:25,770 --> 01:05:28,100
-可否給我們...　-我是奇頓醫生
- Can you give us...? - I'm Dr. Frederick Chilton.

737
01:05:28,440 --> 01:05:29,900
-怎樣寫法？　-奇特的奇...
- Spell it? - That's C-H...

738
01:05:31,670 --> 01:05:33,500
你是奇頓醫生的組員嗎？
Are you with Dr. Chilton's group?

739
01:05:33,880 --> 01:05:36,240
我剛在外面見到他
Well, I just saw him outside, sir.

740
01:05:36,580 --> 01:05:39,740
不能有太多人接近萊達，我們接到死亡恐嚇
Access to Lecter is limited. We've received death threats.

741
01:05:40,050 --> 01:05:41,520
我明白的
I understand, sir.

742
01:05:47,760 --> 01:05:49,250
登記和把武器放下
Log in and check your weapon.

743
01:05:50,830 --> 01:05:52,950
我不能獨自邀功的
I can't take all the credit myself.

744
01:05:53,260 --> 01:05:55,460
馬丁參議員，司法部，聯邦調查局
Senator Martin, Justice Department, FBI...

745
01:05:55,760 --> 01:05:59,060
巴爾的摩州立醫院的人員，最困難就是...
folks at the Baltimore State Hospital. Now for the hard part:

746
01:05:59,400 --> 01:06:01,030
逮捕那個疑匪
Apprehending the suspect.

747
01:06:01,700 --> 01:06:03,670
對不起，我要趕飛機了
Excuse me, I have to catch a flight.

748
01:06:08,010 --> 01:06:10,100
指揮台，我是傑各警員
Command desk, Officer Jacobs.

749
01:06:16,080 --> 01:06:17,450
（路易斯・法蘭飛禽，猥褻）

750
01:06:17,790 --> 01:06:18,840
（鐵）

751
01:06:19,150 --> 01:06:22,150
-他們說的是事實嗎？　-什麼？
- Is it true what they're saying? - Huh?

752
01:06:23,230 --> 01:06:25,190
他是個吸血殭屍？
He's some kind of vampire?

753
01:06:27,530 --> 01:06:29,620
他們沒有替他取名
They don't have a name for what he is.

754
01:06:30,830 --> 01:06:32,390
小姐，你知道規矩的吧？
You do know the rules, ma'am?

755
01:06:33,270 --> 01:06:35,500
知道，我以前盤問過他
Yes, I've questioned him before.

756
01:06:39,110 --> 01:06:39,940
去吧
Go ahead.

757
01:07:17,610 --> 01:07:19,410
克麗絲，晚安
Good evening, Clarice.

758
01:07:21,150 --> 01:07:23,710
你可能想要回你的畫吧
I thought you might like your drawings back.

759
01:07:26,520 --> 01:07:28,350
直到你有自己的景觀
Just until you get your view.

760
01:07:29,260 --> 01:07:31,380
真是周到
How very thoughtful.

761
01:07:32,430 --> 01:07:35,060
還是在你們破案前，克勞福派你來...
Or did Jack Crawford send you for one last wheedle...

762
01:07:35,430 --> 01:07:37,560
說最後一次的花言巧語？
before you're both booted off the case?

763
01:07:38,170 --> 01:07:40,260
不，是我自己想來的
No. I came because I wanted to.

764
01:07:45,070 --> 01:07:47,370
人家會說我們在戀愛呢
People will say we're in love.

765
01:07:51,650 --> 01:07:54,010
安克斯島
Anthrax Island.

766
01:07:54,350 --> 01:07:57,150
真是有心思，克麗絲
That was an especially nice touch, Clarice.

767
01:07:57,520 --> 01:07:58,350
你畫的？
Yours?

768
01:07:59,220 --> 01:08:00,190
是
Yes.

769
01:08:00,460 --> 01:08:01,920
對
Yeah.

770
01:08:02,660 --> 01:08:04,280
很好
That was good.

771
01:08:04,660 --> 01:08:06,420
但我同情可憐的凱瑟琳
Pity about poor Catherine, though.

772
01:08:06,800 --> 01:08:08,760
滴答...
Ticktock, ticktock, ticktock.

773
01:08:09,030 --> 01:08:11,660
你的字謎有破綻了
Your anagrams are showing, doctor.

774
01:08:12,670 --> 01:08:14,070
路易斯・法蘭？
Louis Friend?

775
01:08:14,900 --> 01:08:18,000
是硫化鐵，也叫做黃銅鐵
Iron sulfide, also known as fool's gold.

776
01:08:18,540 --> 01:08:22,270
克麗絲，你的毛病是，你要活得輕鬆一點
Oh, Clarice, your problem is, you need to get more fun out of life.

777
01:08:22,910 --> 01:08:25,710
你在巴爾的摩時說了真話
You were telling me the truth back in Baltimore, sir.

778
01:08:26,080 --> 01:08:27,410
現在繼續吧
Please continue now.

779
01:08:28,150 --> 01:08:30,520
我看過那些檔案了，你看過嗎？
Well, I've read the case files. Have you?

780
01:08:31,020 --> 01:08:33,990
你要緝拿他的資料都在裡面
Everything you need to find him is there in those pages.

781
01:08:34,290 --> 01:08:37,020
-那麼教我怎樣做　-首要的原則
- Then tell me how. - First principles, Clarice.

782
01:08:37,390 --> 01:08:40,380
是簡易，讀馬可・奧勒利烏斯吧
Simplicity. Read Marcus Aurelius.

783
01:08:40,700 --> 01:08:44,030
凡事都問：它是什麼？
Of each particular thing, ask: What is it in itself?

784
01:08:44,370 --> 01:08:45,990
它有什麼本質？
What is its nature?

785
01:08:46,600 --> 01:08:50,330
你尋找的這個人，他做什麼？
What does he do, this man you seek?

786
01:08:52,010 --> 01:08:53,130
殺害女人
He kills women.

787
01:08:53,440 --> 01:08:56,270
不，那是次要的
No. That is incidental.

788
01:08:56,910 --> 01:09:02,440
他主要是做什麼？他殺人是為了滿足什麼？
What is the principle thing he does? What needs does he serve by killing?

789
01:09:03,080 --> 01:09:04,210
憤怒
Anger...

790
01:09:05,950 --> 01:09:09,910
社會認同和性困惑
social acceptance and sexual frustration...

791
01:09:10,190 --> 01:09:11,020
不是！
No!

792
01:09:11,760 --> 01:09:13,730
他貪圖
He covets.

793
01:09:14,660 --> 01:09:16,130
那是他的本性
That is his nature.

794
01:09:16,230 --> 01:09:18,960
我們怎樣才會開始貪圖？
And how do we begin to covet, Clarice?

795
01:09:19,830 --> 01:09:22,330
我們是否去尋找貪圖的東西？
Do we seek out things to covet?

796
01:09:23,070 --> 01:09:24,800
嘗試回答吧
Make an effort to answer now.

797
01:09:25,170 --> 01:09:27,510
不是，我們只是...
No, we just...

798
01:09:27,840 --> 01:09:31,070
我們看見日常的東西就開始貪圖
No, we begin by coveting what we see every day.

799
01:09:31,380 --> 01:09:34,580
你可有感到一些眼睛在盯著你？
Don't you feel eyes moving over your body, Clarice?

800
01:09:35,420 --> 01:09:38,680
你的眼睛，又可有尋找你要的東西？
And don't your eyes seek out the things you want?

801
01:09:39,520 --> 01:09:41,750
有的，請你告訴我吧
All right, yes. Now, please tell me how.

802
01:09:42,060 --> 01:09:43,390
不
No.

803
01:09:44,260 --> 01:09:46,060
輪到你告訴我了
It is your turn to tell me, Clarice.

804
01:09:46,430 --> 01:09:48,760
你再沒有假期可哄騙我了
You don't have any more vacations to sell.

805
01:09:49,560 --> 01:09:51,930
為何你離開那個牧場？
Why did you leave that ranch?

806
01:09:52,370 --> 01:09:56,330
我們沒有時間再玩這一套了
Doctor, we don't have any more time for any of this now.

807
01:09:56,600 --> 01:09:59,000
但我們的時間觀念是不同的
But we don't reckon time the same way, do we?

808
01:09:59,340 --> 01:10:01,040
你只有這麼多的時間
This is all the time you'll have.

809
01:10:01,410 --> 01:10:03,600
稍後吧，請聽著，我們只有五個...
Later. Please listen. We've only got five...

810
01:10:03,780 --> 01:10:06,940
不，我現在要聽
No! I will listen now.

811
01:10:09,180 --> 01:10:11,980
父親被殺後，你十歲就成了孤兒
Your father's murder orphaned you when you were 10.

812
01:10:12,350 --> 01:10:17,050
你去了蒙大拿，跟一些養羊馬的表親同住，之後呢？
You went to live with cousins on a sheep and horse ranch in Montana. And?

813
01:10:19,460 --> 01:10:21,590
我在一個早上跑掉了
And one morning I just ran away.

814
01:10:22,430 --> 01:10:25,830
不是的，什麼驅使你離開？
Not "just," Clarice. What set you off?

815
01:10:26,130 --> 01:10:27,600
你在什麼時候出發？
You started at what time?

816
01:10:28,470 --> 01:10:29,660
很早，天還沒亮
Early, still dark.

817
01:10:29,970 --> 01:10:32,440
有東西吵醒你，是不是一個夢？
Then something woke you. Was it a dream?

818
01:10:32,770 --> 01:10:33,800
是什麼？
What was it?

819
01:10:35,410 --> 01:10:37,040
我聽到一種奇怪的聲音
I heard a strange noise.

820
01:10:38,410 --> 01:10:39,680
是什麼？
What was it?

821
01:10:40,350 --> 01:10:41,510
是...
It was...

822
01:10:42,820 --> 01:10:44,220
尖叫聲
screaming.

823
01:10:45,890 --> 01:10:48,450
像小孩的尖叫聲
Some kind of screaming, like a child's voice.

824
01:10:49,160 --> 01:10:50,520
你怎麼做？
What did you do?

825
01:10:51,160 --> 01:10:52,390
我下樓
I went...

826
01:10:52,690 --> 01:10:55,250
走出屋外
downstairs. Outside.

827
01:10:57,530 --> 01:11:00,000
我偷進了殼倉
I crept up into the barn.

828
01:11:00,340 --> 01:11:03,460
我很害怕看進去，但又必須看
I was so scared to look inside, but I had to.

829
01:11:04,670 --> 01:11:07,870
你看見什麼？克麗絲？
And what did you see, Clarice? What did you see?

830
01:11:09,410 --> 01:11:10,610
一些羔羊
Lambs.

831
01:11:11,910 --> 01:11:13,440
它們在尖叫
They were screaming.

832
01:11:14,150 --> 01:11:16,780
他們在宰殺那些羔羊？
They were slaughtering the spring lambs?

833
01:11:17,490 --> 01:11:19,080
而它們在尖叫
And they were screaming.

834
01:11:20,560 --> 01:11:22,110
那你就跑掉了？
And you ran away?

835
01:11:22,460 --> 01:11:26,150
不是，最初我想釋放它們
No. First I tried to free them.

836
01:11:26,960 --> 01:11:29,290
我打開它們的閘門
I opened the gate to their pen.

837
01:11:29,600 --> 01:11:32,930
它們只是站在那裡，很困惑的，不肯走
They just stood there, confused. They wouldn't run.

838
01:11:33,230 --> 01:11:35,630
但你可以走，你也走了，是不是？
But you could and you did, didn't you?

839
01:11:36,540 --> 01:11:39,840
是的，我抱起一隻羊就拔足逃跑
Yes. I took one lamb and I ran away as fast as I could.

840
01:11:40,140 --> 01:11:41,800
你去哪裡？
Where were you going, Clarice?

841
01:11:42,140 --> 01:11:44,980
不知道，我沒有食物和水
I don't know. I didn't have any food, any water...

842
01:11:45,350 --> 01:11:47,840
而且當時很冷，非常冷
and it was very cold. It was very cold.

843
01:11:50,190 --> 01:11:51,240
我以為...
I thought...

844
01:11:52,220 --> 01:11:54,690
我以為，至少可救到一隻羊
I thought if I could save just one...

845
01:11:56,790 --> 01:11:58,260
但它很重
but he was so heavy.

846
01:11:59,490 --> 01:12:00,890
真的很重
He was so heavy.

847
01:12:06,300 --> 01:12:10,070
我走不了幾里路，警長的車就把我截住
I didn't get more than a few miles when the sheriffs car picked me up.

848
01:12:13,410 --> 01:12:17,540
牧場主人很生氣，把我送到博斯曼的路德會孤兒院
The rancher was so angry he sent me to a Lutheran orphanage in Bozeman.

849
01:12:18,450 --> 01:12:20,280
我再沒看過那個牧場了
I never saw the ranch again.

850
01:12:21,150 --> 01:12:23,740
你的羊又怎麼樣？
What became of your lamb, Clarice?

851
01:12:25,820 --> 01:12:27,010
他們把它殺了
They killed him.

852
01:12:27,490 --> 01:12:29,650
有時你仍會驚醒，是嗎？
You still wake up sometimes, don't you?

853
01:12:30,020 --> 01:12:31,580
在黑暗中醒來...
Wake up in the dark...

854
01:12:32,390 --> 01:12:35,090
聽到那些羔羊的尖叫聲？
and hear the screaming of the lambs?

855
01:12:35,830 --> 01:12:36,850
是的
Yes.

856
01:12:38,430 --> 01:12:41,100
你相信如果把凱瑟琳救了出來
And you think if you save poor Catherine...

857
01:12:41,440 --> 01:12:44,890
可以令它們停止尖叫是嗎？你相信如果凱瑟琳活著...
you can make them stop, don't you? You think if Catherine lives...

858
01:12:45,210 --> 01:12:48,330
你就不會在黑夜中...
you won't wake up in the dark ever again...

859
01:12:48,610 --> 01:12:51,340
再被那些恐怖的羊聲驚醒了
to that awful screaming of the lambs.

860
01:12:52,650 --> 01:12:53,910
我不知道
I don't know.

861
01:12:54,750 --> 01:12:55,980
我不知道
I don't know.

862
01:12:57,790 --> 01:13:00,080
謝謝你，克麗絲
Thank you, Clarice.

863
01:13:00,390 --> 01:13:01,860
謝謝你
Thank you.

864
01:13:02,260 --> 01:13:04,090
告訴我他的名字
Tell me his name, doctor.

865
01:13:11,200 --> 01:13:13,360
是奇頓醫生吧
Dr. Chilton, I presume.

866
01:13:14,070 --> 01:13:15,540
我相信你們是認識的
I think you know each other.

867
01:13:17,870 --> 01:13:19,340
好吧
Okay.

868
01:13:20,040 --> 01:13:22,100
-我們找到她了　-我們走吧
- We found her. - Let's go.

869
01:13:22,380 --> 01:13:24,000
醫生，輪到你了
It's your turn, doctor.

870
01:13:24,550 --> 01:13:26,070
-出去　-說出他的名字
- Out! - Tell me his name.

871
01:13:26,410 --> 01:13:29,110
抱歉，我接到命令，要把你送上飛機
Sorry, ma'am, I've got orders to put you on a plane.

872
01:13:29,450 --> 01:13:30,540
走吧
Come on, now.

873
01:13:30,890 --> 01:13:32,680
勇敢的克麗絲
Brave Clarice.

874
01:13:33,190 --> 01:13:36,650
那些羔羊停止尖叫時，你會告訴我的，是嗎？
You will let me know when those lambs stop screaming, won't you?

875
01:13:36,960 --> 01:13:38,650
說出他的名字
Tell me his name, doctor!

876
01:13:38,990 --> 01:13:40,220
克麗絲
Clarice!

877
01:13:41,700 --> 01:13:43,320
你的檔案
Your case file.

878
01:13:45,130 --> 01:13:46,160
餵！
Hey!

879
01:13:48,400 --> 01:13:49,800
再見，克麗絲
Goodbye, Clarice.

880
01:14:56,070 --> 01:14:57,700
醫生，準備好就來吧
Ready when you are, doc.

881
01:14:58,240 --> 01:15:00,260
請等一會
Just another minute, please.

882
01:15:09,180 --> 01:15:11,520
那個混蛋竟然要再吃晚飯
Son of a bitch demanded a second dinner.

883
01:15:11,820 --> 01:15:13,510
還要極生的羊排
Lamb chops, extra rare.

884
01:15:13,860 --> 01:15:18,320
不知他早餐要吃什麼？動物園裡的怪物？
Wonder what he wants for breakfast? Some damn thing from the zoo?

885
01:15:28,700 --> 01:15:29,530
（化學噴霧）

886
01:15:40,010 --> 01:15:41,380
兩位，晚安
Good evening, gentlemen.

887
01:15:41,950 --> 01:15:43,510
好的，醫生，蹲下吧
Okay, doc. Grab some floor.

888
01:15:43,850 --> 01:15:45,840
跟以前的程序一樣
Same drill as before, please.

889
01:15:52,760 --> 01:15:54,960
龐畢探員，準備好了
Ready when you are, Sergeant Pembry.

890
01:16:11,680 --> 01:16:12,740
行了
Okay.

891
01:16:19,490 --> 01:16:20,850
遞給我吧
Hand me that, would you?

892
01:16:26,690 --> 01:16:27,750
謝謝
Thanks.

893
01:16:31,770 --> 01:16:33,600
請小心那些畫
Mind the drawings, please.

894
01:16:37,000 --> 01:16:37,970
謝謝你
Thank you.

895
01:17:02,600 --> 01:17:05,070
龐畢，小心，他把我扣住
Pembry, watch it, he's cuffed me!

896
01:17:11,840 --> 01:17:13,200
天啊
Jesus Christ!

897
01:18:32,120 --> 01:18:34,450
龐畢探員，準備好就來吧
Ready when you are, Sergeant Pembry.

898
01:18:44,000 --> 01:18:45,760
究竟什麼回事？
What is this shit?

899
01:18:48,400 --> 01:18:49,960
有人上了五樓？
Did somebody go up on five?

900
01:18:50,300 --> 01:18:53,970
-沒有人上過去　-叫龐畢，叫他告訴...
- No, nobody went up. - Call Pembry. Ask him to tell...

901
01:18:57,010 --> 01:19:01,000
CP，五樓有槍聲，重復，五樓有槍聲
CP, shots fired on five. Repeat, shots fired on five.

902
01:19:01,280 --> 01:19:02,510
戴德警官
Sergeant Tate!

903
01:19:03,220 --> 01:19:04,710
去，五樓有槍聲
Proceed. Shots fired on five.

904
01:19:05,420 --> 01:19:06,940
天啊！
Holy shit!

905
01:19:07,290 --> 01:19:08,950
-怎麼了？　-混蛋！
- What the hell? - Bitch!

906
01:19:09,460 --> 01:19:10,290
閉嘴！
Shut up!

907
01:19:10,730 --> 01:19:11,780
波比，拿避彈衣來
Bobby, get the vest.

908
01:19:12,090 --> 01:19:13,460
是，警官
Right, sarge.

909
01:19:13,900 --> 01:19:15,950
-布萊迪，霍華，掩護　-看！
- Brady, Howard, cover... - Look!

910
01:19:18,900 --> 01:19:20,300
它停了
It stopped.

911
01:19:21,700 --> 01:19:23,230
封鎖方圓十幢樓的範圍
Seal off a 10-block radius.

912
01:19:23,570 --> 01:19:26,370
召特種部隊和救護車來，快點！
Get me the SWAT team and an ambulance, double quick.

913
01:19:26,740 --> 01:19:27,800
我們上樓去
We're going up.

914
01:19:56,940 --> 01:19:58,340
龐畢？
Pembry?!

915
01:19:59,910 --> 01:20:01,270
鮑爾？
Boyle?!

916
01:20:14,390 --> 01:20:15,650
天啊！
Oh, God!

917
01:20:22,900 --> 01:20:23,890
去
Go.

918
01:20:31,770 --> 01:20:33,070
-沒有人　-沒有人
- Clear. - Clear.

919
01:20:33,370 --> 01:20:34,670
指揮站
Command post.

920
01:20:35,210 --> 01:20:36,610
兩個警員死了
Two officers down.

921
01:20:36,940 --> 01:20:38,310
-沒有人　-沒有人
- Clear! - Clear!

922
01:20:38,880 --> 01:20:39,970
警官，萊達不見了
Lecter's gone, sarge.

923
01:20:40,280 --> 01:20:41,940
囚犯失蹤了
Prisoner is missing.

924
01:20:42,280 --> 01:20:43,650
鮑爾的配槍不見了
Boyle's gun is gone.

925
01:20:44,090 --> 01:20:46,490
重復，萊達持械失蹤了
Repeat. Lecter is missing and armed.

926
01:20:46,790 --> 01:20:48,450
他拿走了床鋪
He stripped the bed.

927
01:20:49,020 --> 01:20:51,650
可能用來做繩，搜查所有窗戶
Might be making a rope. Check all the windows.

928
01:20:51,990 --> 01:20:54,190
救護車在哪裡？
Where the fuck is my ambulance?

929
01:20:54,760 --> 01:20:56,130
他仍活著的
He's alive.

930
01:20:56,330 --> 01:20:59,030
戴德警官，他仍活著！
Sergeant Tate! He's alive!

931
01:20:59,500 --> 01:21:02,590
扶著他，撫摸他的手，跟他說話
Get ahold of him and feel his hands. Talk to him!

932
01:21:03,200 --> 01:21:04,170
說什麼？
What do I say?

933
01:21:04,440 --> 01:21:07,200
他是龐德吉姆，跟他說話，該死
It's Jim Pembry. Now talk to him, damn it!

934
01:21:08,280 --> 01:21:10,440
萊達持械失蹤了
Lecter is missing and armed.

935
01:21:10,750 --> 01:21:14,410
-龐畢...你聽到我嗎？　-他拿了鮑爾的配槍
- Pembry. Pembry, can you hear me? - He took Boyle's gun.

936
01:21:14,780 --> 01:21:17,750
龐畢發過一槍，萊達可能中了槍的
Pembry got off one round. There's a chance Lecter's hit.

937
01:21:18,020 --> 01:21:19,780
繼續呼吸吧
Keep breathing in and out.

938
01:21:20,150 --> 01:21:23,590
你做得很好，你沒事的
You're doing a good job. You look real good there.

939
01:21:24,360 --> 01:21:27,090
對，你沒事的
Yeah, you look... Look real good.

940
01:21:44,250 --> 01:21:45,410
-準備了嗎？　-來吧
- You ready? - Let's go!

941
01:21:45,410 --> 01:21:47,110
-我們來吧　-好的，走吧
- Let's do it. - Okay, let's go!

942
01:21:58,560 --> 01:22:00,620
很好，你支持得住的
Looking good. You're gonna make it.

943
01:22:00,900 --> 01:22:02,730
沒事的
Everything's just fine.

944
01:22:03,100 --> 01:22:05,220
-我要作靜脈注射　-乳酸林格注射液
- I need that IV now! - Lactated Ringer's.

945
01:22:05,530 --> 01:22:07,800
可否拿那條帶子來？氧氣在哪裡？
Can we get the strap? Where's the oxygen?

946
01:22:08,100 --> 01:22:11,700
老兄，情況很好，鎮定一點
Doing good, buddy. That's right. Stay with me here.

947
01:22:13,170 --> 01:22:15,800
他不行了，去樓下，快點
We're losing him! Downstairs, quickly!

948
01:22:16,280 --> 01:22:17,640
抬起！
And up!

949
01:22:18,980 --> 01:22:19,970
-電梯！　-這邊
- Elevator! - This way!

950
01:22:20,250 --> 01:22:22,770
-讓開！　-讓開！
- Out of the way! - Get out of the way!

951
01:22:26,690 --> 01:22:28,150
CP叫戴德
CP to Tate.

952
01:22:28,460 --> 01:22:31,150
收到，我是戴德
Roger, lieutenant. Tate here.

953
01:22:31,530 --> 01:22:34,020
我現在乘電梯送龐畢下來
I'm on the elevator bringing Pembry down.

954
01:22:34,630 --> 01:22:36,430
他看來支持得住
He seems to be hanging on.

955
01:22:37,300 --> 01:22:39,320
最高的三層樓封鎖了
Top three floors secured.

956
01:22:39,930 --> 01:22:41,930
主要樓梯封鎖了
Main stairwell secured.

957
01:22:42,970 --> 01:22:44,700
我們相信他在二樓
We think he's on two.

958
01:22:58,120 --> 01:23:00,210
戴德，你聽到嗎？
Tate, you still with me?

959
01:23:01,960 --> 01:23:04,290
我們頗肯定他在二樓
We're pretty sure he's somewhere on two, sir.

960
01:23:04,490 --> 01:23:06,290
通話暫時完畢
That's all for now. Over.

961
01:23:25,880 --> 01:23:28,350
他在電梯頂
He's on the roof of the elevator.

962
01:23:31,150 --> 01:23:32,380
好的，大家來
Okay, guys.

963
01:23:49,100 --> 01:23:49,930
我看到他
I see him.

964
01:23:50,570 --> 01:23:52,840
他的手旁邊有一支槍，他沒有動
There's a gun by his hand. He's not moving.

965
01:23:53,770 --> 01:23:56,400
-警告，我們要生擒他　-知道
- One warning. We need him alive. - Got it.

966
01:23:57,680 --> 01:23:58,800
萊達？
Lecter?

967
01:23:59,210 --> 01:24:00,980
把雙手放在頭上
Put your hands on your head.

968
01:24:03,520 --> 01:24:04,850
向腿射一槍
One in the leg.

969
01:24:16,060 --> 01:24:17,460
沒有動靜
No movement.

970
01:24:18,830 --> 01:24:21,390
約翰，不要開槍，我們要進入電梯
Johnny, hold your fire. We're coming into the car.

971
01:24:22,000 --> 01:24:23,490
我們會打開蓋口
We're opening the hatch.

972
01:24:24,470 --> 01:24:25,300
小心他的手
Watch his hands.

973
01:24:25,670 --> 01:24:28,440
如果有開火，會是我們發的，確定
If there's any fire, it'll come from us. Affirm.

974
01:24:28,810 --> 01:24:29,780
明白
Got it.

975
01:24:56,000 --> 01:24:57,770
孟斐斯醫院，這是26號車
Memphis General, this is Unit 26.

976
01:24:58,140 --> 01:25:00,610
我們會送來一名五十歲男警
We're inbound with a 50-year-old male officer...

977
01:25:00,910 --> 01:25:02,930
他面部有嚴重割傷
with severe facial lacerations.

978
01:25:03,240 --> 01:25:06,510
他全身出現抽搐，情況嚴重
He had grand mal seizure activity. He's postdictal now.

979
01:25:06,580 --> 01:25:08,640
-收到　-重要器官情況良好
- I copy. - Vital signs are good.

980
01:25:08,950 --> 01:25:10,470
-血壓是130/90　-90？
- Pressure is 130l90. - Ninety?

981
01:25:10,820 --> 01:25:12,880
對，是90，脈搏84
Yeah, that's right, 90. Pulse, 84.

982
01:25:13,250 --> 01:25:15,450
我們給他注射了乳酸林格注射液
We got him on lactated Ringer's running...

983
01:25:15,760 --> 01:25:17,950
病人正在吸十公升的氧氣
and the patient is on 10 liters of oxygen.

984
01:25:19,190 --> 01:25:20,250
小心！
Watch it!

985
01:25:24,700 --> 01:25:27,960
那輛救護車在孟斐斯機場一個車庫里被發現
The ambulance was found in a parking garage at Memphis Airport.

986
01:25:28,300 --> 01:25:29,670
工作人員死了
The crew was dead.

987
01:25:30,870 --> 01:25:32,360
他還殺了一名遊客
He killed a tourist too.

988
01:25:32,710 --> 01:25:34,400
拿了他的衣服和鈔票
Got his clothes, cash.

989
01:25:34,980 --> 01:25:36,600
他可能在任何地方
By now he could be anywhere.

990
01:25:36,980 --> 01:25:38,810
-他不會來對付我的　-真的？
- He won't come after me. - Oh, really?

991
01:25:39,180 --> 01:25:40,200
他不會的
He won't.

992
01:25:40,780 --> 01:25:42,370
我不能解釋
I can't explain it.

993
01:25:42,750 --> 01:25:44,880
他認為那樣做很無禮
He would consider that rude.

994
01:25:45,450 --> 01:25:47,110
都完了，她已經死了
It's over. She's dead.

995
01:25:47,490 --> 01:25:48,980
這不是你的錯
It's not your fault.

996
01:25:49,320 --> 01:25:53,820
萊達說，我們需要捉拿他的資料都在這裡，但我不能...
Lecter said everything we need to catch him with is here, only I can't...

997
01:25:54,160 --> 01:25:55,790
萊達醫生說了很多話
Dr. Lecter said a lot of things.

998
01:25:56,700 --> 01:25:57,820
雅戴，他在這裡的
He's here, Ardelia.

999
01:26:27,560 --> 01:26:29,360
這是萊達的筆跡嗎？
Is this Lecter's handwriting?

1000
01:26:31,570 --> 01:26:35,830
這樣雜亂地分布現場，不是有點極度隨意嗎？
"Doesn't this random scattering of sites seem desperately random?

1001
01:26:36,140 --> 01:26:39,770
像個差勁說謊者的精心策劃？漢尼拔・萊達
Like the elaboration of a bad liar? Ta. Hannibal Lecter."

1002
01:26:40,140 --> 01:26:43,010
「極度隨意」，他是什麼意思？
"Desperately random." What does he mean?

1003
01:26:43,380 --> 01:26:46,110
可能根本不是隨意，是有一個模式的
Not random at all, maybe. Like there's a pattern here.

1004
01:26:47,380 --> 01:26:50,510
但並沒有模式，不然電腦也會發現
But there's no pattern or the computers would've nailed it.

1005
01:26:50,820 --> 01:26:53,120
屍體甚至是不依次序被發現的
They're even found in random order.

