You're all right. Where is he?

1179
01:45:47,720 --> 01:45:50,520
我怎麼知道？快救我出去！
How the fuck should I know? Just get me out of here!

1180
01:45:50,890 --> 01:45:53,950
凱瑟琳，你靜一點，叫那只狗別吵
Catherine, you've gotta be quiet! Now, shut that dog up!

1181
01:45:54,260 --> 01:45:56,250
快救我出去！
Just get me out of here!

1182
01:45:57,430 --> 01:45:58,490
我的天
Oh, my God.

1183
01:46:01,030 --> 01:46:05,050
凱瑟琳，我會救你的，但你聽著
Catherine, I'm gonna get you out. But right now, you listen to me.

1184
01:46:05,260 --> 01:46:07,230
我要離開一會，很快回來
I've gotta leave. I'll be right back

1185
01:46:08,240 --> 01:46:11,370
不，不要丟下我，你這個婊子，別走！
No! Don't you leave me here, you fucking bitch! No!

1186
01:46:11,510 --> 01:46:12,980
不要丟下我！
Don't you leave me here!

1187
01:46:13,250 --> 01:46:15,840
這個傢伙是瘋的！
This guy is fucking crazy!

1188
01:46:18,350 --> 01:46:23,050
等一下，我要離開這裡
Wait! I gotta get out of here!

1189
01:46:24,690 --> 01:46:25,520
求求你！
Please!

1190
01:46:25,890 --> 01:46:30,450
凱瑟琳！其他的探員會很快到達的
Catherine! The other officers will be here any minute now.

1191
01:46:30,800 --> 01:46:34,390
不要走！求求你
Wait! Don't go! Please!

1192
01:46:34,730 --> 01:46:35,930
別吵！
Quiet!

1193
01:46:38,340 --> 01:46:40,810
天啊...
Oh, God! Oh, God!

1194
01:50:04,940 --> 01:50:06,410
（恐怖）

1195
01:50:06,710 --> 01:50:08,910
（比爾剝下第五個人的皮）

1196
01:50:36,840 --> 01:50:39,210
-你沒事吧？　-小事，不要緊，我沒事
- You okay? - Gunpowder. It's nothing, I'm okay.

1197
01:50:39,510 --> 01:50:42,480
史達琳探員，你怎麼追查到水牛比爾在這裡的？
Agent Starling, how did you track Buffalo Bill here?

1198
01:50:42,750 --> 01:50:46,310
（司法部聯邦調查局）

1199
01:50:48,850 --> 01:50:51,580
克麗絲・史達琳
Clarice M. Starling.

1200
01:50:53,890 --> 01:50:55,090
恭喜你
Congratulations.

1201
01:51:08,710 --> 01:51:11,340
昂利・史蒂文
Ernest W. Stevens.

1202
01:51:29,230 --> 01:51:30,960
特種探員克麗絲・史達琳！
Special Agent Starling!

1203
01:51:31,530 --> 01:51:33,290
-特種探員麥普　-有電話找你
- Special Agent Mapp. - Phone call.

1204
01:51:33,670 --> 01:51:34,890
謝謝，失陪
Thank you. Excuse me.

1205
01:51:35,200 --> 01:51:36,360
史達琳
Starling.

1206
01:51:39,310 --> 01:51:42,000
替我們拍照好嗎？
Pilch, could you take our picture?

1207
01:51:42,410 --> 01:51:43,400
好的
Sure.

1208
01:51:45,410 --> 01:51:47,470
我只想說聲恭喜
I just wanted to say congratulations.

1209
01:51:47,910 --> 01:51:51,350
我不擅應酬，所以我要走了
I'm no good at this kind of thing, so I'm gonna duck out of here.

1210
01:51:51,950 --> 01:51:53,440
好的
Okay. Sure.

1211
01:51:55,090 --> 01:51:56,610
謝謝，葛先生
Thank you, Mr. Crawford.

1212
01:52:04,560 --> 01:52:06,690
令尊今天定會很驕傲
Your father would've been proud today.

1213
01:52:10,100 --> 01:52:11,690
別忘了接聽電話
Don't forget your phone call.

1214
01:52:16,480 --> 01:52:17,740
史達琳
Starling.

1215
01:52:18,080 --> 01:52:19,540
克麗絲...
Well, Clarice...

1216
01:52:20,210 --> 01:52:22,610
那些羔羊停止尖叫了嗎？
have the lambs stopped screaming?

1217
01:52:23,150 --> 01:52:24,210
萊達醫生？
Dr. Lecter?

1218
01:52:24,480 --> 01:52:27,450
不必追蹤這個電話，我不會講太久
Don't bother with a trace. I won't be on long enough.

1219
01:52:31,020 --> 01:52:33,080
萊達醫生，你在哪裡？
Where are you, Dr. Lecter?

1220
01:52:33,360 --> 01:52:35,050
我不打算找你了
I have no plans to call on you.

1221
01:52:35,430 --> 01:52:37,790
有了你，這個世界更加有趣
The world's more interesting with you in it.

1222
01:52:38,430 --> 01:52:41,260
你保重，日後報答我吧
So you take care now to extend me the same courtesy.

1223
01:52:41,630 --> 01:52:44,100
我不能作那個承諾的
You know I can't make that promise.

1224
01:52:44,670 --> 01:52:46,930
但願我們可以多聊一會
I do wish we could chat longer...

1225
01:52:48,340 --> 01:52:50,900
但我找了個老朋友吃晚飯
but I'm having an old friend for dinner.

1226
01:52:52,510 --> 01:52:53,670
再見
Bye.

1227
01:52:54,250 --> 01:52:55,470
萊達醫生！
Dr. Lecter!

1228
01:52:58,080 --> 01:52:59,410
萊達醫生
Dr. Lecter.

1229
01:53:01,720 --> 01:53:03,090
萊達醫生
Dr. Lecter.

1230
01:53:05,120 --> 01:53:06,590
萊達醫生？
Dr. Lecter?

1231
01:53:07,730 --> 01:53:09,020
抱歉，對不起
Excuse me. I'm sorry.

1232
01:53:09,330 --> 01:53:10,850
保安系統安排了嗎？
The security system's set up?

1233
01:53:11,200 --> 01:53:13,720
-我們有嚴密保安的　-謝謝
- We have the big shot security. - I appreciate it.

